1
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:16,460
Grandpa is sending you back to your country.

2
00:02:20,200 --> 00:02:22,120
If you know the way back,

3
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:23,680
you can find your home.

4
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:29,400
Perseverance is victory.

5
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,160
Stop.

6
00:02:31,320 --> 00:02:32,960
All overseas Chinese.

7
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:34,280
China will win.

8
00:02:46,720 --> 00:02:47,640
Hurry up.

9
00:03:23,200 --> 00:03:27,520
We cannot fail the expectations of overseas Chinese.

10
00:03:31,720 --> 00:03:36,840
You must hold on until the day of victory.

11
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:38,520
See for me

12
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:43,320
what victory looks like.

13
00:04:46,520 --> 00:04:47,400
Push hard.

14
00:04:48,080 --> 00:04:48,920
Move out.

15
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:54,360
I sincerely swear

16
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:58,400
to voluntarily join the Nanyang Overseas Chinese Mechanics Returning to Serve Group,

17
00:04:58,400 --> 00:04:59,680
obey assignments,

18
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:01,080
observe discipline,

19
00:05:01,080 --> 00:05:02,400
support the resistance,

20
00:05:02,400 --> 00:05:03,840
be loyal to the motherland,

21
00:05:03,840 --> 00:05:05,240
do my duty,

22
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:06,600
and not fear sacrifice.
